  "description": "<ul> \n  <li><p><strong>Stylish and Versatile Design</strong>\uff1aThis raised garden bed features a sleek and modern design, making it a stylish addition to any outdoor space. It is perfect for creating a beautiful and functional garden area, whether you want to grow vegetables, herbs, flowers, or other plants.</p></li> \n  <li><p><strong>Safe and Comfortable to Use</strong>\uff1aThe raised garden bed is designed with safety in mind. It has protective pads on the corners to prevent accidental injuries, and the edges of the steel plates are polished to avoid cuts. This ensures a safe and comfortable gardening experience.</p></li> \n  <li><p><strong>Healthy Plant Growth</strong>\uff1aThe bottomless design of the raised garden bed allows plant roots to stretch freely and access nutrients more effectively. It also ensures proper drainage, preventing water from stagnating and promoting healthy plant growth.</p></li> \n  <li><p><strong>Durable and Strong Construction</strong>\uff1aMade from high-quality galvanized materials, this raised garden bed is durable and strong. It can withstand various weather conditions and provide a stable and reliable environment for your plants to thrive.</p></li> \n  <li><p><strong>Easy Installation</strong>\uff1aThe raised garden bed is designed for easy assembly. It comes with detailed instructions and gloves, making it simple for one person to set up. You can quickly and effortlessly create your own garden space without any hassle.</p></li> \n </ul> \n <div> \n  <b>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;*Dear customers, most of our products are shipped from our overseas warehouse via FedEx, ensuring fast and reliable delivery.</b> \n  <span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><br></span> \n </div> \n <div> \n  <img src=\"https://cf.cjdropshipping.com/d66c6d52-e724-4694-85d6-6a3f70d15eee.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> \n  <img src=\"https://cf.cjdropshipping.com/0e661d5c-0217-4bbe-aa31-c624aa8b3af2.jpg\" st